Title: Series: Palazzo Granducale in Firenze
Description: Rest on the flight into Egypt, a circular composition after Francesco Albani; the Virgin sits at centre with the sleeping Christ on her lap; St Joseph sits on the left, reading a book; two angels on the right, and three cherubic heads above the group Engraving
Curator's comments: For comment on series see 1861,0608.278. Painting now in the Musée de Peinture et de Sculpture, Grenoble (inv. MG1). See Catherine Puglisi, 'Francesco Albani', Yale University 1999, cat. No. 150.
Acquisition name: Purchased from: A E Evans & Sons
